OL,5, The closure of some petrol stations has
OL,6, reignited a row over lorry driver      
OL,7, shortages in the UK.                   
OL,9,FA "handful" of BP stations, and a small
OL,10,Fnumber of Esso-owned Tesco Alliance    
OL,11,Fstations, were closed on Thursday due  
OL,12,Fto a lack of delivery drivers.         
OL,14,FIt is estimated that the UK is short of
OL,15,Fabout 100,000 HGV drivers - with gaps  
OL,16,Fmade worse by the pandemic and Brexit. 
OL,18,FDowning Street said there was "no      
OL,19,Fshortage of fuel in the UK and people  
OL,20,Fshould continue to buy fuel as normal".
